可以 I @ mention my Aitoearn 团队 members within a Note? Currently, it isn’t possible 到 @ mention 您的 Aitoearn 团队 members though 这个 is something 我们’re con侧边ring 添加ing soon! ### 将会 I be able 到 see who 创建d a Note? Yes. The Note shows the email 添加ress of the person who 创建d the note. ### Who 可以 see the Notes? Once a note is 保存d, it is visible 到 anyone 在 the 组织 who has been given access 到 那个 channel.
